                  ‚àÉ‚àÉT. L ‚ä¢ T1 [d, e] ‚â´ T & L ‚ä¢ T2 [d, e] ‚â´ T.
#L #T0 #T1 #d #e #H elim H -H L T0 T1 d e
[ /2/
